The No-Lose Lottery is designed to value and recognize meaningful Forum contributions in the Hyperion ecosystem. Every two weeks, participants can earn tickets—every 10 points earned equals 1 lottery ticket—for a chance to win prizes.
Your engagement, posts, and helpful activity directly increase your chances to be rewarded. Stay active and let your contributions count!
Thank you all for participating and supporting the Hyperion ecosystem!

